=======================
Comfirm hbeatd - README
=======================
(C) 2012 Comfirm AB

Simple and lightweight heartbeat sensor and pulse. Zero configuration.

Authors:
Jack Engqvist Johansson, Comfirm AB
http://comfirm.se

License:
BSD 3-Clause
See the LICENSE file

Usage
=====
 usage: hbeatd [ -v [-s | -p] ]
  -p	run as heartbeat (pulse)
  -s	run as heartbeat sensor
  -v	verbose mode


